_sText:
Created for the 2021 KSF winter mapping competition in about 2 weeks.
Theme is the alien world of Kepler 452b, an earthlike exoplanet located about 1,400 light years from Earth.

Staged linear with 9 stages taking about 1:00 - 1:10 to complete if run linear. Native momentum zones are included in the map file.
Bonuses by Apexe and Sneakyy
3500 maxvel

All assets were created from scratch in 3dsmax for this map exclusively. Most textures are modified from textures.com. Naturally the skybox is Mr.Who's.

Big thanks to Shawn Olson for creating Wall Worm Model Tools!
